<br>
I have in the past had very successful experiences with the entire spectrum of Wisdom casters. Every one brings solid complementary skills and strengths to the table. <br>
<br>
INT casters also seem to fit in well with Magicians.<br>
<br>
What I'd like to know a little more about is how well people have found grouping with our friends the Melee classes. It seems very difficult without adding healing support. I have successfully grouped with a Paladin, but their healing is very solid and with T-Rods we got by just fine. <br>
<br>
I have duoed quite well with a well-equipped Monk also. I suspect that with their decent lifetaps and Fear, Shadow Knights would make a reaonsble if not ultimate partner.<br>
<br>
Has anyone successfully duoed with Ranger, Rogue or Warrior? I would like to think that a Magician could grab anyone who was LFG and team up to take down mobs efficiently, but to be honest I dont see how it would work out with these classes.<br>
<br>
Thoughts? <p><table width = 200 border = 0>
